  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf.\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Six people who attacked MP Dolawatta's house were arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Western Province Southern District Crime Division says that 6 people including a student studying for a diploma in a higher education institution were arrested for attacking the Kaduwela Bomiriya home of Mr. Premanath C. Dolawatta, Member of Parliament and causing damage to the property.",
        "According to the police, there was a loss of 70 lakh rupees to the house and property due to that attack.",
        "A police officer said that among those arrested are a tricycle driver and a welder and all the suspects are aged between 16 and 20 years.",
        "The police say that this group of suspects had attacked the MP's house and damaged the property in connection with the Galumodara incident on the last day of May.",
        "It has been revealed in the police investigation that the Thiroda car driver who is among those arrested led the attack on the MP's house and the higher education student was the first person to break the door and enter the house by hitting the gate with an iron rod."
      ],
